highlights.text: Saran has the most spots on Top Songs Thailand. “รออยู่อย่างนั้น” is the highest at #41.
“ไฟเย็น” by YOUNGOHM has been on Top Songs Thailand the longest, at 966 days straight.
“ถ้าวันนั้น(IF I)” by URBOYTJ and เล็ก รัชเมศฐ์ is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Thailand, up 58 spots at #116.
